{"tid":1201944,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"今次會去既人 不如一齊組織隊伍","createTime":"2019-06-11T07:20:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-11T11:22:49.000Z","uid":20353,"like":36,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"798ee136cce362673b1ee522be2b8fa25425bebc","tid":1201944,"uid":20353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T07:20:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/HK1841\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FHK1841&d=0xAgwAOhMzbM3o1MPcLVDyHfnck7qU2fF1mVfqY7ZMk%3D&h=fec8aed5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/HK1841</a><br />\n有意請聯絡 留低性别同想做既崗位<br />\n<br />\n暫時建議:<br />\n夠150人就正式組織<br />\n30人為一組<br />\n15人為一隊<br />\n5人沖鋒 6人護衛 2人救援 2人指揮<br />\n即最少組成到5組(10隊)先正式成立<br />\n<br />\n分組目的係確保安全保密 盡量減少影響既人數<br />\n<br />\n真係出唔到黎唔緊要<br />\n希望大家提供更多意見<br />\n幫助係出面既兄弟"},{"pid":"c8ce65d3a0e2fd79d7bdcec9f4fe897704cfdd6a","tid":1201944,"uid":71502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T07:21:54.000Z","msg":"今晚點安排"},{"pid":"7ba5791d3d49e6b499edc03702001b488de2bdf6","tid":1201944,"uid":20353,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T07:24:25.000Z","msg":"外面話10點開始<br />\n我諗或者我地12點集合？<br />\n到時逐個個别地確認身份 避免有鬼係入面"},{"pid":"f7905fb1d99e26e62f40b7b7ab76dab27cfc5953","tid":1201944,"uid":47776,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T07:29:12.000Z","msg":"小心有鬼<br />\n點check係唔係狗嘅身份係重點<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一陣比班狗混咗入黎就麻煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3858651fe9dac7e6f9febca0a3ae5f73accb7677","tid":1201944,"uid":20353,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"f7905fb1d99e26e62f40b7b7ab76dab27cfc5953","tid":1201944,"uid":47776,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T07:29:12.000Z","msg":"小心有鬼<br />\n點check係唔係狗嘅身份係重點<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一陣比班狗混咗入黎就麻煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T07:37:19.000Z","msg":"岩 其中一個重點係分鬼<br />\n到時係現場會識别身份<br />\n希望大家提供更多意見<br />\n<br />\nbtw 意見就係依到share 方便討論<br />\n採納邊啲就唔會係到講"},{"pid":"3e9130851aab4878df765757d19ba84b18ef51ff","tid":1201944,"uid":129139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T07:39:33.000Z","msg":"<strong>集中辯論投票</strong><br />\n<br />\n[公投]究竟幾時出嚟？<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1199505\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1199505</a>"},{"pid":"7afe2dcccf00da1c4608e6c3d36440415122ec38","tid":1201944,"uid":20353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T07:44:52.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"8657fd5a2d97702b737579fdbb2d7c8aa1ccebc4","tid":1201944,"uid":20353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T07:53:31.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"3656d4a79e01287225e4e6796c9b1998a7492636","tid":1201944,"uid":20353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T08:16:43.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"8ee99ff572786cade5150afcd4e2690731b4c178","tid":1201944,"uid":233009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T08:19:09.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"34c772893eb2b7160c6ff15e7cd79ae03371064d","tid":1201944,"uid":206080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T08:19:54.000Z","msg":"全部係獨立個體 咁啱距離近啫"},{"pid":"a0c6628bee9cc112064d7af23eb0c24b04be6dc1","tid":1201944,"uid":189187,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T08:22:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed97ad6bf0f96401af8cbbac8efc657d84984c7d","tid":1201944,"uid":20353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a0c6628bee9cc112064d7af23eb0c24b04be6dc1","tid":1201944,"uid":189187,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T08:22:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T08:26:1